    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Schneider Electric India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Backend Developer to strengthen our Bhubaneswar-based team.\n\nAbout Schneider Electric India:\nSchneider Electric India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Learning & development budget\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Schneider Electric India!",
